description.lostinfinity.jei.ingots=Ingots can be forged through the Ingot refinery within Nonexistence.
description.lostinfinity.jei.ingots.kyvorium=Created by right-clicking the Meta Materializer with a Clovinite Power Bank while a Vellorium Ingot, Kylaxium Ingot, and Xerovium Ingot is in the closest box, an Organic Plate, Corrupted Root, and Giant Tentacle in the middle box, as well as a sacrifice of 3 mobs or a single player in the farthest box.
description.lostinfinity.jei.ingots.biosynthium=Created by right-clicking the Meta Materializer with an Adhesive Fibre while an Olysium Ingot, Detherium Ingot, and Phytrosium Ingot is in the closest box, a Gloom Bulb, Pickle, and Anthocite in the middle box, as well as a sacrifice of 3 mobs or a single player in the farthest box.
description.lostinfinity.jei.ingots.malicium=Created by right-clicking the Meta Materializer with an External Clovinite Battery while a Noxerium Ingot, Incadium Ingot, and Emberium Ingot is in the closest box, a Ghostly Husk, Flexible Husk, and Corrupted Root in the middle box, as well as a sacrifice of 3 mobs or a single player in the farthest box.
description.lostinfinity.jei.ingots.etherium=Created by right-clicking the Meta Materializer with an Ion Cell while an Olysium Ingot, Xerovium Ingot, and Detherium Ingot is in the closest box, a Photochromic Husk, Ghostly Husk, and Luminescent Stingers in the middle box, as well as a sacrifice of 3 mobs or a single player in the farthest box.
description.lostinfinity.jei.ingots.polarium=Created by right-clicking the Meta Materializer with a Potent Polarcronite while a Xerovium Ingot, Phytrosium Ingot, and Hextorium Ingot is in the closest box, a Volatile Blood, Glowing Globes, and Glowing Organ in the middle box, as well as a sacrifice of 3 mobs or a single player in the farthest box.

description.lostinfinity.jei.machines.gearbox=Must have a Combustion Engine powered next to it. Connect gears to each other where they are each touching (not overlapping)
description.lostinfinity.jei.machines.compressiontable=Found within Nonexistence, system must be unclogged periodically with Carbonic Acid to compress ores
description.lostinfinity.jei.machines.grinder=Using an active Gearbox next to it, grinds down Sunstone by cleaning the "soot" off without touching the red box in the center
description.lostinfinity.jei.machines.engine=Used to Power a Gearbox using Spark Plugs
description.lostinfinity.jei.machines.fusion=Complete the crafting by making a 2x2 of the same block using the pieces provided on the bottom left. Filling the board without completing a square will lead to a full reset of crafting progress
description.lostinfinity.jei.machines.irg=Portal opens when an Inter-dimensional Rift Generator is found 30 blocks away in the Cardinal directions of a center placed Inter-Dimensional Rift Generator, and Eterno Cells are inserted.

description.lostinfinity.jei.chemistryclays.colixium=Crafted by dropping 5 Darksteel Shards, 5 Elastic Tissue, and 5 Super-Mutated Crystals in a 2x2 pool of Concentrated Acid, then right-clicking the Concentrated Acid pool with a Colixium Catenation Pouch.
description.lostinfinity.jei.chemistryclays.phoroxium=Crafted by dropping 5 Auradine, 5 Space Pickle, and 5 Super-Mutated Pelt in a 2x2 pool of Concentrated Acid, then right-clicking the Concentrated Acid pool with a Phoroxium Catenation Pouch.
description.lostinfinity.jei.chemistryclays.laraxium=Crafted by dropping 5 Incandescite, 5 Glow Bulb, and 5 Organic Fuse in a 2x2 pool of Concentrated Acid, then right-clicking the Concentrated Acid pool with a Laraxium Catenation Pouch.

