description.lostinfinity.jei.minigames.overchargedcell=Obtained by right-clicking the Light Tile Game starter block and winning the mini-game then using a Supercharged Cell on the High Powered Charger in the Middle Labyrinth
description.lostinfinity.jei.minigames.eternalemberstargenerator=Obtained by right-clicking the Emberstar Charger starter block with an Unpowered Emberstar and winning the mini-game using Electrified Quartz in the Top Labyrinth
