description.lostinfinity.jei.minigames.georedirectionorb=Obtained by right-clicking the Redirection Chamber Game starter block with a Geo-Coordinated Orb and winning the mini-game by turning all arrows red in the Middle Labyrinth
description.lostinfinity.jei.minigames.microstoragepowercluster=Obtained by right-clicking the Power Condenser starter block with 4 Clovenite Power Banks and winning the mini-game in the Middle Labyrinth

description.lostinfinity.jei.minigames.powercontroldisc=Obtained by right-clicking the Power Conduit starter block with a Blank Optical Disc and winning the mini-game in Nonexistence
