description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.gasfilledballoon=Throw and Unstable Balloon in the air and continue to bounce it up without it hitting the ground a total of 8 times
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.lifesynchronizer=Use Effigy Doll on a player then throw the doll into lava
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.giantheart=Use Pulse Charge on a Leviathan then slay it
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.claysupports=Use Clay Terraformer on Sea Clay, then change modes and place blocks in the chosen pattern
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.plasmaticcranium=Kill a player between the beams of a connected Plasma Emitter and Plasma Receiver
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.voidalteredspine=Use Rapid Tunneling Device on a player or Dimensional Trader while within the Infinite Murk
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.astralgenerator=Place down a Nebulous Beacon and protect it while it charges
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.astralorgan=Use Scroll of Reconstruction on 6 different Whispers and defeat the boss
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.reconfiguredmatter=Use the Matter Recombiner within the Infinite Murk
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.stickydarksteel=Feed a Tetherbug a Darksteel
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.organicshadowmatter=Place Fish Chow, right-click it, and follow the fish until the item drops
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.velocitizedfemur=Use Rocket Strapped Explosive on a player in the Overworld or a Dimensional Trader within the End
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.magicconch=Use Silver Tokens on Treasure Hunter and finish their challenge
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.chewedskull=Kill an entity by bringing a Skyre nearby with a Beacon of Darkness and right-clicking an entity with it to get the Skyre to attack them
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.heartoflight=Transport Wisp from the Radiant Tree to the Lumino Tree in Nonexistence and click it with a Lightbinder
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.aligneddisc=Create a 4x4 of Rift Entangled Tile in the Overworld, then switch to the Infinite Murk and right-click the same Rift Entangled Tiles with a Power Analyzer
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.murkyclay=Give a Grubber a Jar of Murky Syrup
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.voidsplitbone=Use Vacuum Container on a Void Flower in the Infinite Murk then use an Elastic Thread to connect the block to an entity
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.voidflower=Grow a Moon Flower in the Overworld, it will become a Void Flower in the Infinite Murk
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.branchofenergy=Transport Wisp from the Radiant Orange Tree to the Rebirth Blue Tree
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.electricalaccelerator=Right-Click Main Power Terminal Block within Nonexistence and complete the given Blueprints and return them to the block
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.crushedbones=Crush an entity under The Crusher
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.toxicsporesample=Throw Spike Balls at Galaxy Vine Spore
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.darkworlddatachip=Right-Click an Eye Battery in Nonexistence with 5 Organic Wire, 10 Organic Plate, 20 Gloominessence Cubes, and 3 Basic Storage Chip, and right-click the Eye Battery again
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.florocite=Find Lumcubes in the Luminessence area of Nonexistence and right-click them with a bio-energiser
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.heartofdarkness=Transport Wisp from Light to Darkness and right-click with the Darkbinder next to the Archlum Logs
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.mutantfungus=Click Fungus with Bio-Corruption Powder and have a Screecher hit it
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.knifeincarnation=Click the Knife Icon, and defeat the Galaxy Spire in the Nonexistence Boss Room
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.swordincarnation=Click the Sword Icon, and defeat the Galaxy Spire in the Nonexistence Boss Room
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.bombincarnation=Click the Bomb Icon, and defeat the Galaxy Spire in the Nonexistence Boss Room
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.warpeddisc=Use Geo-Coorelator to find Traveller 3 times and then kill it
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.clovinitepowerhub=Use External Clovinite Battery on Hyper Generator, throw 10 Clovinite Power Bank and 20 Electron Recycler into the Hyper Melder
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.explosivegoosample=Collect Goo thrown at you by a Hurler with a bottle
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.essence=Activate Idol in Nonexistence with Illumination Stone
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.acidbucket=Collect Concentrated Acid in Nonexistence near Mossy Astro Rock
description.lostinfinity.jei.misc.eternocell=Charge Unpowered Cells in Nonexistence using the Cell Charger block

description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.etherflower=Grow an Etherstock up by right-clicking the top of the stock with Magic Biopowder until it becomes an Ether Flower
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.lifeforce=Right-Click another player with a Super-Charged Injection and slay them
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.radionfragment=Obtained by charging a Radion Pillar and right-clicking it
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.fossils=Use a Fossil Finder to discover these fossils within the Shadow Sea
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.scroll=Given to you when you lower a Screamer's total lives
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.translationbook=Obtained by right-clicking the Ancient Symbol Interpreter with a Magical Book and winning the mini-game in the Labyrinth
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.anthocite=Find Blightcubes in the Luminessence area of Nonexistence and right-click them with a bio-energiser
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.watchfuleye=Throw Spike Balls at the corresponding Colored Tentacle Eyes
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.elementstone=Activate an Unpowered Element Stone
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.firefeather=Use Heat-Resistant Tongs on a Flutterfyre
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.concentratedvenom=Right-Click a Acidback that has been Poisoned with a Glass Bottle
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.cursedemerald=Formed when a Deviant with Skull Shot strikes an Emerald Ore block
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.droidlocation=Data of Droid death given based on the vanilla world it died in or if it was fighting a Deviant
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.superheatedingot=Formed when a Deviant Ghast's fireball strikes an Iron Ore block
description.lostinfinity.jei.unknown.starlitglobe=Randomly given by Dimensional Trader when trading Deviant Egg, Deviant Beef, Deviant Milk, or Deviant Porkchop


